        "Description": "Arrghh, these rich folks keep stealing all of our treasures! They don&apos;t even allow you to shoot your &quot;mates&quot; once or else they will come running for your exact position! Let&apos;s show them what it feels like to be a true pirate!\rMake sure you&apos;ve set up &quot;the trap&quot;! Once that&apos;s done, get rid of them in a way so that they will know the pain of a stump for a leg!",
